Government Circular No: Apna-0223 / P.No.295 / Papu-15
7th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Building, Near Crawford Mocket,
Government Notification, General Administration Department, No: SRV-2016 / Q. No. 281/12, dated 21st June, 2021.
Government Circular, Water Supply and Sanitation Department, No: Apna-0223 / P.No.295 / Papu-15 dated 10.01.2024
The General Administration Department conducts regular examinations of officers / employees of the government service every year.

The Subsidiary Policy for preparation and publication has been notified vide Notification No. 1 in this regard. The tentative merit list dated 01.01.2024 for the category of Assistant Geophysicist (Group-B) in Ground Water Surveillance and Development System under reference No.2 was published. Considering the objections received in this regard, a provisional final report showing the status of the Assistant Geophysicist (Group-B) category in the Ground Water Surveillance and Development System as on 01.01.2024 has been prepared. The above mentioned documents are attached to this circular as Annexure-A.
The mother of the deceased. The Special Leave Petition No. will be subject to the result in 28306/2017.

The Commissioner, Ground Water Surveillance and Development System, Ground Water Bhawan, Shivajinagar, Pune is requested to bring to the notice of all concerned who are retired from the department and on deputation from the establishment of the department, who are working in your department and are included in the list of issues with this circular.
